  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718122/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201406/c4eb420a-edc1-4d02-9c43-969dc82f4ef1.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><strong><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\" target=\"_blank\">《英闻天天译》</a></strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">是一档沪江部落的原创翻译互动节目（</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/162103461876/\"><strong>戳去参与节目&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">），主持人提供翻译参考文本，对大家递交的翻译作品进行点评，和大家共同进步！本期节目选</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">取的是关于</span>经济影响文学<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana, helvetica; line-height: 28px;\">一则英文报道，让我们一起在翻译中关注</span><font style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">。</font></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"border-left-width: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-image: none;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i3.s.yun.hjfile.cn/entry/201501/fd14b3d9-4181-4ba3-b57a-1a5d0817a6e8.jpg!topic\" /></span></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"border-left-width: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-image: none;\"><strong>SUMMARY：</strong></span></span></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-variant: normal; white-space: normal; float: none; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-style: normal; line-height: 28px;\">近日，医生说儿童药物由于颜色鲜艳和糖衣的口感，导致一些儿童用药过量，并要求药品生产商改变药物的口感和外观~~</span></span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">CONTENT：</strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWith 12 million bottles sold each year, Calpol is a medicine <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cabinet\" target=\"_blank\">cabinet</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/staple\" target=\"_blank\">staple</a> in most homes, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/soothe\" target=\"_blank\">soothing</a> childhood aches and pains thanks to its main ingredient &ndash; <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/paracetamol\" target=\"_blank\">paracetamol</a>.<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBut now a leading doctor has warned that children could be at risk of accidental <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/overdose\" target=\"_blank\">overdose</a> from Calpol and other brightly coloured drugs that &lsquo;look more like <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/milkshake\" target=\"_blank\">milkshake</a> than medicines&rsquo;.<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDoctors say that Calpol&rsquo;s <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/syrup\" target=\"_blank\">syrup</a>-sweet strawberry taste and pink colouring also makes it &lsquo;almost irresistible&rsquo; to some <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/youngster\" target=\"_blank\">youngster</a>s.<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&lsquo;Some children go to alarming lengths to get their hands on it while their parents&rsquo; backs are turned,&rsquo; said one.<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHealth professionals have now urged Calpol&rsquo;s manufacturers to make the medicine less appealing to youngsters to prevent accidental overdose of paracetamol, which can cause serious <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/liver\" target=\"_blank\">liver</a> damage and, in rare cases, prove <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fatal\" target=\"_blank\">fatal</a>.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,100,0);\"><strong>【沪江英语小编】</strong></span>大家在查看主持人提供的翻译版本前，可以先自己进行尝试翻译练习，只有在不断的翻译中翻译能力才能有所提升哦！<br />\n\t轻松注册沪江，马上参与<strong><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\">【英闻天天译】</a></strong>节目练翻译&rarr;<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/810ca373cf4442a188b39dd8ff64425f.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>本期节目参考译文：</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128,128,128);\">（参考译文由该节目主持人提供，仅供参考，欢迎大家讨论）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>参考译文1：</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">Calpol是大多数家庭医药箱的必备品，由于其主成分&mdash;&mdash;扑热息痛，它能够缓解儿童疼痛，每年销量1200万瓶。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t但是一名主要的医生警告说儿童可能处于偶尔过量服用Calpol和其他着色鲜艳的药物而处于极大的危险中，这些药物&ldquo;看起来与其说是药，更像奶昔&rdquo;。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t医生们说Calpol的草莓甜味和粉色的糖衣也是很多小孩子对它&ldquo;毫无抵抗&rdquo;。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t一位医生说，&ldquo;当父母不注意的时候，一些孩子竭尽全力要拿到糖浆&rdquo;。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t健康专家现在要求Calpol生产商将药物做的不那么迎合孩子，以避免由于意外过量服用扑热息痛。过量服用会导致严重的肝损伤，在极端情况下还会有致命危险。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>参考译文2：</strong></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">英国Calpol小儿糖浆年销量1,200万瓶，是大多数家庭医药箱中的压箱宝。由于其主要成分为扑热息痛，该药品具有舒缓疼痛的疗效。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t然而现在却有位医生警告道：由于Calpol糖浆及其它一些药品色彩鲜艳，看起来更像是奶昔而非药品，可能使儿童面临不小心饮用过量的危险。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t许多医生说，Calpol糖浆的草莓口味和粉粉的色彩对一些儿童来说简直无法抗拒。其中一位医生说：&ldquo;一些小孩趁父母不备便去拿这种糖浆，其不遗余力的劲头令人咋舌。&rdquo;<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t目前，保健专业人士已敦促Calpol制造商，要求他们将药品做得不那么吸引儿童，以阻止扑热息痛意外过量摄入，因为扑热息痛过量会导致严重的肝损伤，少数情况下甚至会致命。 </span></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/162103461876/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0);\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718122/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718122\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720594/\">四六级查分，你魔性了吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p587662/\">每天要问自己的5个问题 你的答案是什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720237/\">不运动就能瘦 每天多吃些浆果吧！ </a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p710048/\">外媒看中国 屌丝是什么能吃吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p710637/\">外媒看中国 女人二十岁最爱吃零食</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720792/\">山羊or绵羊？哭晕的“歪果仁”终于明白了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p701248/\">科学告诉你：屏奴时代已经来临！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p595656/\">成功人士在午餐时间会做的10件事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 